767
00:36:19.264 --> 00:36:20.438
I need to destroy it.

768
00:36:20.439 --> 00:36:21.917
What's the matter. Linda?

769
00:36:21.918 --> 00:36:24.006
You're afraid people might see
the real you for once?

770
00:36:24.007 --> 00:36:25.443
Shut up.

771
00:36:25.444 --> 00:36:27.575
Linda. that video will
never see the light of day.

772
00:36:27.576 --> 00:36:28.663
You have my word on it.

773
00:36:28.664 --> 00:36:29.751
Your word.

774
00:36:29.752 --> 00:36:31.971
He's supposed to be dead.

775
00:36:31.972 --> 00:36:35.192
If that ever gets out.
I'll be ruined.

776
00:36:35.193 --> 00:36:36.497
Give me the phone. now!

777
00:36:36.498 --> 00:36:40.022
Linda. you don't want
to hurt anyone. OK?

778
00:36:40.023 --> 00:36:42.634
You just think that you're out
of options. but you're not.

779
00:36:42.635 --> 00:36:44.418
Whatever you've said.
whatever you've done.

780
00:36:44.419 --> 00:36:46.072
it can be forgiven.

781
00:36:46.073 --> 00:36:48.030
There is a chance at redemption.

782
00:36:48.031 --> 00:36:51.599
but that chance goes away
if you don't put the gun down!

783
00:36:54.168 --> 00:36:55.734
I'm... I'm sorry.

784
00:36:55.735 --> 00:36:59.651
I'm so sorry.

785
00:37:14.144 --> 00:37:15.493
I know you have
a lot of questions.

786
00:37:15.494 --> 00:37:16.711
but it's been a long day.

787
00:37:16.712 --> 00:37:19.192
So right now. have a drink.
Take a bath.

788
00:37:19.193 --> 00:37:22.326
Tomorrow. someone's going to
reach out about next steps.

789
00:37:22.327 --> 00:37:24.023
OK?

790
00:37:24.024 --> 00:37:25.720
OK.

791
00:37:41.694 --> 00:37:43.825
Knock. knock.

792
00:37:43.826 --> 00:37:45.740
Hey. you're still here.

793
00:37:45.741 --> 00:37:47.568
Yeah. I was just
writing up a report.

794
00:37:47.569 --> 00:37:50.049
And don't worry. I left out
the bit where you yelled at me.

795
00:37:50.050 --> 00:37:52.879
Well. you know.
stay away from my servers.

796
00:37:54.489 --> 00:37:56.795
Now I know.

797
00:37:56.796 --> 00:37:59.363
Ugh. how do we even
write up the things

798
00:37:59.364 --> 00:38:02.235
that we see in this job anyway?

799
00:38:02.236 --> 00:38:03.759
Carefully.

800
00:38:09.591 --> 00:38:11.331
You're hovering again.

801
00:38:12.942 --> 00:38:14.856
I am.

802
00:38:14.857 --> 00:38:17.206
Is there anything else
that you need?

803
00:38:22.952 --> 00:38:25.040
Are you gonna ask me out
or what?

804
00:38:25.041 --> 00:38:26.304
No.

805
00:38:29.045 --> 00:38:30.569
Maybe.

806
00:38:32.571 --> 00:38:34.267
I'm not even sure
I'm allowed to.

807
00:38:34.268 --> 00:38:37.575
you know. given the
boss/employee situation here.

808
00:38:37.576 --> 00:38:40.491
Oh. you think
that I work for you?

809
00:38:40.492 --> 00:38:42.057
Hmm.

810
00:38:42.058 --> 00:38:45.800
Well. I have been told that.
you know.

811
00:38:45.801 --> 00:38:48.195
I'm in charge.

812
00:38:49.327 --> 00:38:50.588
Is that right?

813
00:38:53.331 --> 00:38:57.116
Well. I think that we should
settle this over a drink.

814
00:39:21.271 --> 00:39:22.663
Hey. what's up?

815
00:39:22.664 --> 00:39:24.622
- What are you doing right now?
<i>- Um. nothing.</i>

816
00:39:24.623 --> 00:39:25.623
<i>What's going on?</i>

817
00:39:25.624 --> 00:39:26.624
Turn on channel nine.

818
00:39:26.625 --> 00:39:27.712
What? Why?

819
00:39:27.713 --> 00:39:29.235
<i>Quick. you're gonna love this.</i>

820
00:39:29.236 --> 00:39:30.367
Just calm down.

821
00:39:30.368 --> 00:39:33.979
<i>Why. effective immediately.</i>

822
00:39:33.980 --> 00:39:38.375
<i>I have decided to step down
as CEO of SnapMax</i>

823
00:39:38.376 --> 00:39:39.985
<i>to focus on my family.</i>

824
00:39:39.986 --> 00:39:41.769
- Whoa.
<i>- Yeah.</i>

825
00:39:41.770 --> 00:39:44.076
that's CEO speak for.
"I did some shady stuff.

826
00:39:44.077 --> 00:39:46.774
and now I'm bailing
before anybody finds out."

827
00:39:46.775 --> 00:39:48.472
<i>Noah Cyrus' convoy was attacked</i>

828
00:39:48.473 --> 00:39:51.083
<i>when it varied from the route
at 2200 hours.</i>

829
00:39:51.084 --> 00:39:52.867
Whoa. whoa. whoa. slow down.
Listen to me.

830
00:39:52.868 --> 00:39:55.479
I'm asking you who authorized
the change in the route.

831
00:39:55.480 --> 00:39:56.958
<i>That's what
I'm telling you. sir.</i>

832
00:39:56.959 --> 00:39:58.525
<i>I have it right here.</i>

833
00:39:58.526 --> 00:40:00.701
That's impossible.

834
00:40:00.702 --> 00:40:02.311
Look again.

835
00:40:02.312 --> 00:40:03.487
<i>Records show
the prisoner transport</i>

836
00:40:03.488 --> 00:40:05.271
<i>was given field orders
to reroute</i>

837
00:40:05.272 --> 00:40:08.492
<i>by agent in charge.
Jacob Hasani.</i>

838
00:40:15.021 --> 00:40:16.804
<i>OK. what about BadGuyBuster?</i>

839
00:40:16.805 --> 00:40:18.937
No. I am not
creating an account.

840
00:40:18.938 --> 00:40:20.025
<i>BexFiles.</i>

841
00:40:20.026 --> 00:40:21.330
<i>That's a good one.</i>

842
00:40:21.331 --> 00:40:23.115
StoneColdBex.

843
00:40:23.116 --> 00:40:24.333
<i>It's not your worst.</i>

844
00:40:24.334 --> 00:40:25.117
<i>You've had worse.</i>

845
00:40:25.118 --> 00:40:26.640
<i>All right. your turn.</i>

846
00:40:26.641 --> 00:40:30.165
What about SecretPrisonGuard...

847
00:40:30.166 --> 00:40:31.558
<i>No.</i>

848
00:40:31.559 --> 00:40:34.518
Ooh. SnackMan.

849
00:40:34.519 --> 00:40:35.954
<i>SnackMan?</i>

850
00:40:35.955 --> 00:40:38.696
OK. I like that.
I can get down with SnackMan.

851
00:40:40.307 --> 00:40:43.178
Well. SnackMan. my food is here.

852
00:40:43.179 --> 00:40:46.225
so I'm gonna say good night.

853
00:40:46.226 --> 00:40:48.053
<i>I'll see you tomorrow. OK?</i>

854
00:40:48.054 --> 00:40:49.968
OK. StoneColdBex.

855
00:40:49.969 --> 00:40:53.319
<i>See you then.</i>
- Good night.

856
00:41:04.418 --> 00:41:06.419
Hi. Shane.

857
00:41:06.420 --> 00:41:08.552
We need to talk.

